Caye Home Furnishings, an international manufacturer of custom home furniture, will open a new plant in Taylorsville.  The company plans to invest $1.4 million and create 128 jobs during the next three years.  The announcement was made possible in part by a $250,000 grant from the One North Carolina Fund.
